---
title: Tarragon Chicken & Wheat Berry Salad with Radishes, Dried Cherries & Almonds
description: Tarragon's citrus and anise notes give ordinary chicken salad extra finesse. Tart dried cherries, crisp radish, and nutty wheat berries add heartiness and textural intrigue to this revamped classic. Bonus: leftovers make the perfect lunch for work.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/554a34e5fd2cb9324b8b456a.
